{"tid":2073811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環時：國安法的「強光」會將像「雪人」的反對勢力「溶掉」","createTime":"2020-06-21T15:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T03:06:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"368e45a41ac6b279617533c3fbcede0df7db932a","tid":2073811,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》發表社評，認為只要公正客觀看待港區國安法草案，都會得出結論，北京真心希望將一國兩制認真維護下去，又認為宣揚港區國安法將埋葬一國兩制的鼓噪，就像張牙舞爪的雪人，經不起事強光的反復照射，那些抵制港區國安法的勢力，必將越來越孤立，進行的只是無勝算的搏鬥。<br />\n<br />\n社評說，中央和內地非常愛護一國兩制，根本無因為憤怒於香港的一些破壞性極端力量，而產生另起爐灶的衝動，無論那些勢力及背後的華盛頓等，接下來做甚麼，將一國兩制繼續推行下去，都是中央和內地社會的理性選擇和不變決心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1315870&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1315870%26csid%3D261_341&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=92a716fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1315870&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc7b8061bca6f160348b89a27e78098a1b85fe4","tid":2073811,"uid":41545,"like":93,"dislike":3,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"得 你咪撚縮 我要見足光版強光呀屌"},{"pid":"36f6925226535b43b2fbceca9a8b77ae81d27d02","tid":2073811,"uid":21713,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"好尷尬。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4a6786201648a2f0136884a634c10fef1b5586","tid":2073811,"uid":41873,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"上面打完飛機未"},{"pid":"2b27ba9ce2a30d60ec9f389f3874b68306d25461","tid":2073811,"uid":164374,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"見倒標題以為係老納 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fe0f283c10f01445e7067d18ba69